{"tid":2512254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普支持者退役女軍人國會示威中身亡 家屬擬求償千萬美金","createTime":"2021-05-01T14:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T14:17:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7cb8903882e86e3fc458e921610f8f1a013dc1","tid":2512254,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統大選落幕後，川普支持者於1月6日闖入美國國會，整起暴動造成傷亡，其中一名川普支持者、美國空軍退伍軍人巴比特（Ashli Babbitt）遭國會警察槍擊身亡。巴比特的家屬近日指出，將會控告開槍的警察，並上訴聯邦法院，求償千萬美金賠償。<br />\n<br />\n ....<br />\n<br />\n其中被警方槍擊身亡的巴比特，曾在美國空軍服役14年，生前她是川普的支持者，不停在社群平台上表態支持川普。<br />\n<br />\n律師羅伯特（Terry Robert）替巴比特家屬代理這起案子，他近日強調，警察該做的是逮捕巴比特，而不是向她開槍；羅伯特透露，將會上訴聯邦地區法院，求償千萬美金，更稱自己知道目前仍未公開的警察名字，巴比特家屬也將會提告警方過失殺人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3517667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517667&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=44f37da8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3517667&h=6e0b0be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3517667</a>"},{"pid":"05ec16b8e2a71dfea2fbff9f308d37de4caeda99","tid":2512254,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ccaf1d5246f20f74fd8cbbd0103eca299cfc53e","tid":2512254,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"2bc4a4ad3d8b3b12036b7348c400da8d53f300ee","tid":2512254,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}